definitions.definition: An Anglo-Saxon kingdom in the Northeast of England ; in full, Kingdom of Northumbria .
A vaguely defined geographic area of England , often synonymous with North East England .

main_definition: ( historical ) An Anglo-Saxon kingdom in the Northeast of England ; in full, Kingdom of Northumbria .
secondary_definitions: ( informal ) A vaguely defined geographic area of England , often synonymous with North East England .
